  "title": "Sales Coordinator [Central, B2B, Electronics Industry] - WCAN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Coordinate and process various sales-related activities</li>\n  <li>Prepare delivery orders and sales invoices</li>\n  <li>Manage customer interactions, including creating quotations, invoicing, and scheduling deliveries</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with B2B corporate sales processes</li>\n  <li>Process sales orders and monitor order status to ensure timely delivery and accurate tracking</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Knowledge of the semiconductor and electronic components industry</li>\n  <li>Basic understanding of supply chain and logistics operations</li>\n  <li>Proficient in IT skills, including advanced Excel functions (VLOOKUP, Pivot Tables) and ERP systems (e.g., SAP)</li>\n  <li>Experience working within a multinational team environment</li>\n  <li>Ability to build and maintain customer trust</li>\n  <li>Strong communication skills with the ability to engage at all organizational levels and work independently</li>\n  <li>Capable of multitasking and adapting to changing priorities</li>\n  <li>Skilled in managing multiple cases simultaneously and responding promptly to unexpected issues</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel: Nyon Hock Sen (Aden)</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24124070</p>",
